{"tid":2136312,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭指DQ議員可延任 譚耀宗稱只是特區政府「諗法」 促內地設票站供港人投票","createTime":"2020-08-02T05:18:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-02T05:35:03.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"fb595b1529686510c6aa7c67c94d4a79d473df82","tid":2136312,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T05:18:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200802/2HJODPW5TL2ZMPWKK7DCWB6O4A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200802%2F2HJODPW5TL2ZMPWKK7DCWB6O4A%2F&d=aFheyUS8Hi5o9a%2F4VMBAnTbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=5f14481b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200802%2F2HJODPW5TL2ZMPWKK7DCWB6O4A%2F&h=4492a3a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200802/2HJODPW5TL2ZMPWKK7DCWB6O4A/</a><br />\n<br />\n全國人大常委會本月8至11日開會料討論香港押後立法會選舉一年的議會「真空期」問題，雖然特首林鄭月娥認為可由現屆議會過渡一年，被DQ的4名民主派同時可續任，但身兼人大常委的民建聯譚耀宗未表贊同，強調這只是特區政府的「諗法」，反問：「人大常委會係咪都係咁睇呢？」他亦再度拋出多項預料有利建制派選情的投票建議，包括大灣區居民在內地投票等，認為選管會未來一年「應該諗得到」如何解決相關問題。"},{"pid":"1dc0e2963a97c0d59b13c54a9d0f4a7646412edf","tid":2136312,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T05:19:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4e37b39eecbd4821be34fe043016fac73d2d0648","tid":2136312,"uid":15697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T05:20:58.000Z","msg":"喺支那境內可以投票係好危險嘅諗法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n懷疑譚耀忠危害國家安全"},{"pid":"dd5d81488e2fa1fcb6310a0e7ed646ee9dbd0b85","tid":2136312,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T05:21:14.000Z","msg":"你係人大唔好扮唔關你事"},{"pid":"a117ef965240fc2321f386f14123efd9e3b5bf18","tid":2136312,"uid":33373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb595b1529686510c6aa7c67c94d4a79d473df82","tid":2136312,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02